text: "Wrap Her Up" is a 1985 song by Elton John. It was taken from his 19th studio album Ice on Fire. George Michael sang backing vocals. It had limited success worldwide. It went to number 12 in the United Kingdom, number 20 in the United States, number 22 in Australia and number 26 in Canada.
